Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of a sudden,\Nyou took my hand in yours{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that we wouldn't\Nget separated in the crowd{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so happy I couldn't squeeze\Nyour hand very tightly in return{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day, I realized I was in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We started out as just friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now let's cross that boundary line{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And take off together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hold my feelings back\Nanymore It hurts so much I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, I can't lie to myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is embarrassing to ask, but{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please accept everything about me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, now and forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"The Poison Doujin of Horror" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Super Manga"\N"Resurrection Series"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doujin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that's Taishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Super Manga"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be... Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doujin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, Great Eimi sneaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "sneaker," it's "stalker."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't wait until\NComipa for my new issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and came here as an\Nillustrial spy, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "industrial spy."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, either way,\Nyou still didn't use it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well too bad! I haven't even finished\Nthe rough draft for this manuscript yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So make like a tree and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Make like a tree and leave."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it, stop correcting\Nme every single time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you even\Ndoing here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever do you mean, Eimi Ohba?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that I\Nalways show up without any reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, are you sure\Nyou should be ignoring the stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doujin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Freeze!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at that, Eimi Ohba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of it! You'll get\Nhit with its poison waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Super Manga"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the doujin of\Nhorror, the Poison Doujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who looks at\Nthe poison manga inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the Great Eimi Ohba,\Nwill give my opinion of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes?\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi ya! Kazuki, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some nice refreshments today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number-one ranked choice for\Nrefreshments among manga authors,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the yakiniku boxed lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eimi? And even Aya too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unusual, for the three of\Nyou to get together so close to Comipa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, Taishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know why these three\Nyoung ladies have gathered here at Elsinore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taishi, what in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, My Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly I was enticed by the\Nallure of the elusive refreshment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Doujouen yakiniku boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything\Nabout the boxed lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you shouldn't look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrade Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you do not\Nknow of the Poison Doujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Doujin? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you've\Nentered the doujin world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet you do not\Nknow of the Poison Doujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's as foolish as trying to talk\Nabout popular songs from the Showa era
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without knowing about Taro Hitofushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Doujin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the doujin of horror,\Nand once you turn its pages,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you lose 100 days off\Nof your doujin life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 days? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about what\NTaishi's talking about too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that's\Nwhy the three of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the name of the\Ncircle on the back cover
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--is our college's manga club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--is our college's manga club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Club Meeting Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the old club meeting hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as creepy as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've never been inside either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't your club\Nhave a club room in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a legend\Nthat I'm a little worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Club Meeting Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do? Quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay behind if you want, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a nice display of\Nresolve, My Brother and My Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taishi! Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our college's Kitora tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A quite appropriate place for us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to mark our first step\Ntoward world conquest, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to find out who's playing\Nthis practical joke about the Poison Doujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Doujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really do intend to\Ngo to the manga club after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the wildness of youth?\NOr is it a tragedy woven by ignorance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will no longer try to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let us go, young men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond this door of horror,\Nas your convictions demand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doujin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Comic Party Revol...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, some "Door of Horror" this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just old and creaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Manga Research Club"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the legend is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're tea bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are ten great horrors of the\Nold club meeting hall. This is number five.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary "black tea cactus."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nightmarish cactus field,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made up of a countless number of tea bags
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that were thrown up on\Nthe ceiling and stuck there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure does sound like a nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that you, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka, Miho, Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. I seriously can't draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panda...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Po... Poison Doujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No.\N--What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You know about it, Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard about it, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's a doujinshi\Nthat the manga club
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made a looong, looong, looong time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that it was banned,\Nand completely burned a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's being distributed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Poison Doujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are the three of\Nyou so shocked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're\Ngoing to the manga club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we plan on doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doujin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison... Doujin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 days?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously think that intimation\Nlike that could possibly work on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the genius, the Great Eimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "intimidation."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you think,\Nthen try drawing one picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To drain or destroy talent, that\Nis the fearsome destructive power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Poison Doujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the talented Eimi\NOhba won't likely be able to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to me,\Nthe genius, the Great Eimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said the manga club's\Nroom is all the way in the back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls seemed really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the Poison Doujin, huh?\NYeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're just like Yu and Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About why those three were so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's not just the Poison Doujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! Number seven\Nof the Ten Great Horrors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the legendary\Nhuge wave, Big Wednesday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how many young\Npeople have been killed by that wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Brother and My Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, arise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must go immediately,\Nfor the sake of our world conquest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tremendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comics?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The huge number of comics and doujinshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the manga and anime\Nclubs buy and buy during the year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pile up until they collapse\Nunder their own weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a horrifying giant wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It collapses on the third Wednesday of\NDecember, which is right before Comipa,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so as the years went by,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it became known as the\Nlegendary giant wave "Big Wednesday."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Kazuki and the others are okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right about now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he could be caught by\Nan evil, horrifying mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inagawa, what was that just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this poison manga.\NHave you seen it somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Seen it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally in the home stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what kind of manga is this\NPoison Doujin everyone's so afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to look at the manga inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't look? Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we won't make it in time at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a horrifying manga\Nthat is so poorly drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is said to destroy the skills of those\Nwho look at it by poisoning their sensitivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.\NThis is Subie's manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See here? Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that bad penwriting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "handwriting."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is definitely Mikage's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, what is Subie thinkin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... You don't\Nthink she was scouted, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skirted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scouted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how could someone\Ndo something so reckless?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've heard about this.\NThis club has a terrifying legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, you don't have\Nto bind the books so neatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our first comeback issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a memorable occasion, so I need\Nto bind them perfectly nice and neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mizuki and Reiko too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, if it isn't Miss Haga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President? Then he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow president of the manga club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Tsukishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making doujinshi again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:17:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the manga research club,\Nare going to regain our former glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have once again begun making\Ndoujin which shall rule the otaku world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things he's saying\Nkind of remind me of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the club been dormant up until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when the manga\Nclub actively produced doujinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the excessively poor quality gave\Nbirth to the legend of the doujin of horror,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which reduces the doujin life span\Nof those who look at it by a 100 days:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the "Poison Doujin."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doujinshi they sent out were\Nall considered to have poison pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sadly, they were completely\Nostracized from the doujinshi world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say, after that, the manga\Nclub was embroiled in a storm of McCarthyism.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making doujin was deemed to\Nbe an evil deed, an immoral act,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it was completely suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sad story...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like it's someone else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you start up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The college authorities\Ndetest literary clubs like vipers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they just decided to turn the\Nmanga research club into a "ghost club"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without even consulting us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're going to kick us\Nout of the old club meeting hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you\Ndecided to make doujin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there was one big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our club has been forced to\Nseclude ourselves for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've lost all of our manga authors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, God has not abandoned us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were stricken with despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a muse of doujin\Nmanga appeared before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. When I saw Subaru's\Nmanga, I had a feeling in my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the manga club could once again\Nclimb to the heights of the doujin world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I immediately invited Subaru to\Nbe the main guest author in our doujinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how the\NPoison Doujin was revived, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the destructively\Nbad tastes which produced
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the poison manga in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it really is true that\Nblood is thicker than water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, let's grab that doujin star together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru will do her best too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, there's one thing\NI don't understand though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was that doujinshi sent\Nto Eimi, Yu and Aya's apartments?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru asked the president to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stars of the doujin world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I really wanted them\Nto help with the next doujinshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought that if I left it\Nwith people in popular circles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our first comeback\Nissue would sell lots and lots,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so those are the first\Nplaces I had him take it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just remembered something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about that "Your doujin life span\Nwill be reduced by 100 days" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we could be doing doujinshi for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so 100 less days isn't all that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you laughing, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason, I'm glad you're happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Super Manga" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doujin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start living together right now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that's missing is time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think we need a place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where we can share our smiles,\Nour tears{\i0}, {\i1}and our free time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was with you,\NI could stay there forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know you don't\Nlike anything complicated{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I still keep on pulling your arms{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally found this 2LDK{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A table set would be fine too{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I think a kotatsu\Nwould be better after all{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time we spend\Njust lying around together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is more important than it sounds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not easy to find someone\Nyou can always accept{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And who will always accept you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you are that person for me, so{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start living together right now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that's missing is time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think we need a place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where we can share smiles,\Nour tears, and our free time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was with you,\NI could stay there forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Say, Ms. Sawada, I know it's rather\Nrude to ask you this all of a sudden, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--What? You want to come watch us work?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- -Yes!\N--What? You want to come watch us work?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- -Yes!\N--Good idea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Good idea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess it would be good for you to take a\Nlook at the professional world at least once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.06,0:23:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it would be\Ngood for you to think about{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how it's the same\Nand how it's different from{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the doujinshi world,\Nand then make your decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm looking forward to it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't mind, but don't\Nbe disappointed, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What do you mean by that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time: "Arise Kazuki,\NIt Is Time for World Conquest."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now is the time for me\Nto decide what I want to do.{\i0}
